**********************************************************
Created By Johnny Fortune [jf@huement.com]
April 11th 2011

Demo Page| http://www.huement.com/code/ajaxPlayer2/

Adapted from jPlayer [http://www.jplayer.org]
**********************************************************

This is a modified jPlayer that allows for the creating and editing of dynamic playlists. Using PHP it searches through an array of given directories and returns JSON formatted results.

Using ajax success functions songs are loaded into the playlist. The full list of commands is currently |

 * Add Songs
 * Delete Songs
 * New Playlist (Reset)
 * Shuffle Playlist
 * Play Forever (infinite play)

If you would like more info, please seek out the jPlayer google group or visit my blog at http://www.huement.com/blog
